metadata.name: Warrior Hanuman #1
metadata.description:
# Background: Earth Element Rock
Just as a rock provides a protective shelter, awakening the Root Chakra will help you feel protected and safe, allowing you to let go of fear and anxiety and fully embrace life.

# Halo: Power To Aquire Needs
You have the power to develop a mindset of abundance. You will believe that you have everything you need to succeed.

# Color: Red
My red color empowers you with passion and devotion. You will stay focused on your spiritual path and will discover a deep love and devotion for the Divine that will cultivate a strong willpower and discipline.

# Adornment: Necklace of Love
I adorn you with the quality of self-compassion, to be kind and gentle with yourself, and to treat yourself with the same Love and care that you would offer to a dear friend.

# Arms: Prayer Hands & Gada
By holding my gada while offering prayer, I remind you to combine strength and devotion in all that you do. Your inner strength will be harnessed with devotion to a higher power, just as I wield the powerful gada while remaining devoted to Lord Rama.



# Crown: Crown of Bliss
Laugh often and don't take life too seriously, for this crown of Bliss brings the quality of finding humor and lightness in every moment.
